<%- include('./partials/header') %>


  <title>About | SkillVouch</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f9f9;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .about-container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .about-container:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: justify;
    }

    .team {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .member {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: 0.3s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .member:hover {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }

    .member h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .back-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .back-btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>


<body>

  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About SkillVouch</h1>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>SkillVouch</strong> — a platform where students, freelancers, and startups connect to
      showcase their skills, find gigs, and grow together. Our mission is to bridge the gap between raw talent and real-world
      opportunities, empowering students to monetize their skills while providing startups with the right talent.</p>

    <p>SkillVouch is designed to be intuitive, fast, and effective. Whether you're looking to gain freelance experience, build
      your portfolio, or find the perfect gig — SkillVouch has got your back!</p>

    <p>Join us on this journey to build a community where talent is valued, growth is limitless, and learning never stops.</p>

    <a href="/" class="back-btn">Back to Home</a>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      console.log("About page loaded!");
    });
  </script>

</body>
<%- include('./partials/footer') %>
